title: (x) Cabin Leader - OWO Banshee Bold {David Rufenacht (self)}
content: It's similar to [ITC Kick](http://web.archive.org/web/20050518125803/http:/www.myfonts.com/fonts/itc/kick/?PREFS_SET%5BRenderSize%5D=48&PREFS_SET%5BRenderString%5D=CABIN+LEADER), but obvioulsy not the same font.
author: bowfinpw
